      "role": "user",
      "content": "stepping back doesn't really change anything though. i'm still here, just watching it happen in real time. it feels like i'm just a passenger on a sinking ship. like, if you know for a fact the ship is going down and there's no lifeboat, why would you even want to stay on board? it just seems like a waste of energy to keep breathing through the panic.",
